---
title: Mexican Smashed Chickpeas & Garlic Rice with Flaked Almonds & Pickled Onion Salsa
description: Don’t be fooled by the ‘smashed’ in our Mexican smashed chickpea bowl, this dish is tranquil and easy, perfect for any hectic weekday night. Soothing rice soaks up an ensemble of tastes from the pickled onion, spiced chickpeas and flaked almonds. So don’t worry, you can sit back and relax into dinner tonight.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
